close_reason: "Completed in combined extension/plugin dedupe PR: canonicalized duplicated extension contract/default sources or routed duplicated plugin/docs inventory to one source. Evidence is recorded on the item and parent pm-rnpb; focused tests, docs/plugin checks, manual temp-project smoke, package dogfood, full release gate, changelog check, GitHub/dependency/security checks, and Sentry/telemetry checks passed."
